pages.text: Contact the SpookEasy Lounge - book this gothic lounge for your next event, find out information, or just let us know how we're doing!

"All Spirits Welcome"
At The Spookeasy Lounge this phrase is more than just some slogan, it is our entire being, our purpose for existing as a business.
​
We wish to create a space where no matter who you are in the "normal" world within our walls you are welcome to be your truest self & be proud of who that person is.
​
Weather you're a Witch, Warlock, Werewolf, Vampire, Elf or any other Fae or even if you're just plain Human; In our establishments you are welcome.
​
No need to bring the mask you wear for the outside world here we want to see the true you, all the scars that make you unique, & if no one else has told you today.
​
YOU ARE LOVED, YOU ARE BEAUTIFUL, YOU ARE CHERISHED & YOU ARE PERFECT
(JUST THE WAY YOU ARE)
Stay Strange
-The Spookeasy
"THE END"
"Where one journey ends another is sure to begin."
​
For us the journey will not end until our community has a place to feel safe no matter how far they travel away from their home here.
​
No matter what the outside world may bring, we will continue to grow and establish a safe space where All Souls Are Welcome!
